entry.tran: (思想)不清楚的，不坚定的，糊涂的
entry.def: If you say that someone is wishy-washy, you are critical of them because their ideas are not firm or clear.

example.ex: If there's anything I can't stand it's an indecisive, wishy-washy customer.
example.tran: 如果说我有什么不能容忍的话，那就是犹犹豫豫、挑来挑去的客户。
